title: South Asia ebook collection
description:
A massive collection of ebooks, mainly .pdf, on South Asia, including India, Pakistan, Bangladesh, Sindh, Baluchistan, Afghanistan, Iran etc. On subjects as varied as History, Politics, Environment, Geography, Literature, Poetry, etc. In short everything related to the area.

List can of course be seen by clicking on the Files: [link] on the top left corner of TPB entry.
